parameters: Hurry! Down here!
A
See those loose wires down there? I need you to get
down there and hold them together for me really quick,
otherwise this thing won't turn on!
ActorMari
Just grab onto the wires?
Are you sure that's safe?
Sure, sure.  Just minor temporal stuff.  Nothing to
worry about.  Now quick, the mall is supposed to open
any minute now!
That was amazing! \n<Nils>
Thanks for helping me.  This thing is EXTREMELY
experimental and I wasn't entirely sure what would
happen there.  It looks like it's working though!
ActorMari
While I was holding it, I could actually
taste the current flowing through me. It
tasted like... the fabric of time itself?
I don't know if that makes any sense.
Oddly enough, that makes sense. When I powered this on,
it punched a wormhole through time itself, and it gets
its power from the potential energy difference between
our time and the future! Pretty neat, huh? \n<Nils>
ActorMari
So I just had experimental wormhole energy
flowing through me?
Yep! Isn't that awesome! \n<Nils>
ActorMari
If you want to see more of this power source, why
don't you come to the Committee of Unionized Legal
Tradesmen meeting on Monday morning? We're discussing
how this thing works and how to supercharge it! \n<Nils>
In fact, we're looking to induct a new member this
week- if you find all ten of us and acquire each of our
induction codewords, we'll induct you, and you get to
vote on what we do with the new power generator! \n<Nils>
ActorMari
Your group is called the Committee of
Unionized Legal Tradesmen... so C.U.L.T.?
Are you sure this isn't a cult?
No, no, I promise we're not a cult!
Why does everyone keep saying that? Just meet me by the
basement doors first thing on Monday and I'll let you
in. Only C.U.L.T. members have keys! \n<Nils>
ActorMari
Yeah, inviting me into your locked basement
to be inducted into a group by speaking
hidden codewords is totally not cult
behavior...
Oh I almost forgot- since you helped so nicely, I'll
give you my codeword for free.  It's "nametag".
That's actually a hint for you, too- you'll need
to pay attention to that at the meeting! \n<Nils>
Well, I'll be waiting for you at the door on Monday!
See you then!  Go ahead and let yourself out. \n<Nils>
B
ActorMari
What a strange encounter...
ActorMari
Okay, I've got the wires!
Alright, great!
Let me boot this up...
Here we go! Hope this works!
ActorMari
I thought you said this was safe-
Wait, I feel something flowing through me,
is that normal- woah!
That's better.
New power source! Pretty cool, huh?
You can come back up here now!
